### Test des routes paramètres GECC

### 1. Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/health

### 2. Inscription d'un utilisateur (pour les tests)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "settings@test.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "fullName": "Settings Test User",
  "role": "architect",
  "companyName": "Test Company",
  "jobTitle": "Architecte"
}

### 3. Connexion
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "settings@test.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 4. Récupérer mes paramètres
GET http://localhost:3000/api/settings
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

### 5. Récupérer des paramètres spécifiques
GET http://localhost:3000/api/settings?keys=theme,language
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

### 6. Récupérer seulement les paramètres publics
GET http://localhost:3000/api/settings?public=true
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

### 7. Mettre à jour des paramètres
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/settings
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "settings": {
    "theme": "dark",
    "language": "en",
    "notifications": {
      "email": true,
      "push": false,
      "project_updates": true,
      "invitations": true
    },
    "dashboard_layout": {
      "widgets": ["projects", "tasks"],
      "columns": 3
    }
  }
}

### 8. Mettre à jour un paramètre personnalisé
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/settings
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "settings": {
    "custom_preference": "ma_valeur_personnalisee",
    "favorite_color": "#ff5733",
    "work_hours": {
      "start": "09:00",
      "end": "18:00",
      "timezone": "Europe/Paris"
    }
  }
}

### 9. Supprimer un paramètre
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/settings/custom_preference
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

### 10. Réinitialiser les paramètres par défaut
POST http://localhost:3000/api/settings/reset
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

### 11. Récupérer les paramètres publics d'un utilisateur
GET http://localhost:3000/api/settings/public/USER_ID_HERE

### 12. Documentation API
GET http://localhost:3000/api/docs
